---
title: Creamy Bacon & Basil Pesto Spaghetti with Tomato Salad & Parmesan
description: The only way to improve the age-old family favourite, pesto pasta, is to add some crispy bacon and sharp Parmesan. With oh-so-many textures and well-loved flavours, this dish is sure to please the whole table!

*Keep an eye out... Due to recent sourcing challenges, we’ve replaced fusilli with spaghetti, which may be a little different to what’s pictured. Don’t worry, your recipe will be just as delicious!*
